set="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg" width="678" height="651" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:651,&quot;width&quot;:678,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:194053,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91b7c971-f769-4005-bff9-afd833e6a646_678x651.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>事实上，丰富的住房是新加坡如此富裕的主要原因之一。</p><p>当然，新加坡拥有如此多住房的原因是该国传说中的“公共”住房政策。那里<a href="https://www.policynote.ca/singapore-housing/">不乏</a><a href="https://www.thearcadiaonline.com/what-is-hdb-housing-and-how-does-it-work/">解释者</a>，但这里是基础知识。新加坡政府拥有大部分土地，并设有一个名为住房发展局（HDB）的政府机构，负责建造大量住房。然后，它以便宜的价格出售这些住房，主要卖给首次购房者（即年轻人）。然后谁可以自由转售它。首次购房者的折扣和政府让价格随着时间的推移缓慢而稳定升值的能力相结合，意味着组屋公寓不仅可以作为廉价的居住场所，而且可以作为一种积累财富的养老金制度。换句话说，在新加坡，用你的家作为居住的地方和用它来创造财富并不矛盾！</p><p>相当了不起。</p><p>好吧，我刚才说的一部分内容实际上并不正确。政府实际上并不向人们出售 HDB 公寓；而是向人们出售 HDB 公寓。它向他们出售 99 年的租约。如果租约还有98年，那就非常接近所有权了，所以当新加坡的制度开始时，它基本上是一个房屋所有权制度（事实上，新加坡的房屋被称为“永久业权”，或私人拥有，从技术上讲是999 年租约！）。请记住，新加坡成立于 1965 年，因此 99 年租约尚未到期。但再过几十年，这将成为一个令人头疼的问题，因为租约到期的人将不得不搬到新公寓。人们现在开始思考那一天，这会<a href="https://theindependent.sg/hdbs-99-year-time-bombs-are-ticking-dont-mess-around-with-them/">扰乱租赁市场</a>并导致一些公寓开始贬值。</p><p>对新加坡政府而言，99年租约是一项毫无意义的政策。只要政府拥有土地，如果需要重建旧建筑，它总是可以让居民搬走——基本上，这就像政府控制公寓协会的公寓一样。为每间公寓增加时间限制，这会让人们在任意日期搬出，这是一个不必要的额外步骤。</p><p>但抛开这个小问题不谈，新加坡的建屋发展局系统对于解决困扰大多数其他国家的住房问题来说绝对是一个令人惊奇的解决方案。基本上，政府拥有和开发土地可以控制住房供应，从而生产充足的经济适用房和可预测的缓慢升值。爱尔兰因<a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/ireland/housing-planning/2023/03/23/irelands-housing-crisis-facts-and-figures-all-you-need-to-know/">住房短缺而臭名昭著</a>，其制药业面临着将制药业输给新加坡的风险——新加坡是美国制药 FDI 的主要竞争对手，原因很简单，新加坡可以建造住房，而爱尔兰则不能。如果我负责爱尔兰，我会拼命寻找某种方式来效仿建屋发展局。</p><p>事实上，如果我也是美国人，我也会寻找效仿 HDB 的方法。事实上，拜登政府一直在<a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/biden-unveils-plan-increase-us-122815341.html">试图通过一项在我看来非常适合新加坡的试点计划</a>：</p><blockquote><p>拜登-哈里斯政府最近宣布了邻里房屋税收抵免，以及为特定首次购房者提供首付援助。该计划旨在为父母也从未拥有过住房的第一代或低财富买家创造一条拥有住房的途径。</p><p>邻里住宅税收抵免尚未获得国会签署。根据白宫 10 月 16 日星期一发表的声明，如果该法案获得通过，将拨款 160 亿美元资金在美国各地建造或修复 40 万套新住宅。此外，该计划还将提供 100 亿美元的首付援助和 1 亿美元用于补贴首次购房者。</p></blockquote><p>美国各州也应该研究类似的计划。</p><p>不管怎样，值得一提的是，并不是每个新加坡人——也不是每个中产阶级——都住在组屋里。尽管这个国家很小，但更远的地方也有一些郊区风格的地区，那里的大部分住房都是低层私人所有。很多看起来像这样： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg" width="1456" height="1934" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1934,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:796690,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa4b3995b-2d23-4199-a293-bd5628ca7fd0_1542x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这不是一座带草坪的宽敞牧场房屋，但它有<em>很大</em>的居住空间，并且有足够的隐私。然而，这种建筑使得一个区域非常密集，即使没有高层建筑。在美国，这当然是一个“缺失的中间”选择。</p><h4>新加坡步行街</h4><p>现在，我要说的是新加坡的城市环境让我困扰的一件事。令人惊讶的是，它的布局以汽车为中心。</p><p>新加坡人大多乘坐火车和公共汽车出行； <a href="https://www.deccanherald.com/world/singapores-car-lite-policy-reduces-car-ownership-to-one-third-down-from-40-in-2013-2758732">只有三分之一</a>的人口拥有汽车。火车系统很棒——虽然不如日本的好，但也没有什么好。步行游览非常方便。</p><p>但是当您四处走动时，您经常会走在一条非常大的街道一侧的狭窄人行道上。例如，这是我在小印度拍摄的照片，这是新加坡最具活力的民族社区之一： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg" width="616" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:616,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:227078,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6e51b7b2-f1d5-4e2a-9680-91f734cd06b8_616x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>主要购物街是一条巨大的四车道道路！当我拍摄这张照片时，交通并不多（部分原因是我一直等到没有汽车阻挡拍摄），但汽车经过的频率足够高，以至于你会吸入大量废气。</p><p>这种情况并不是特别罕见。市中心的大部分地区都布满了比上图大得多<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1722158747043381359">的巨大主干道</a>，而且城市的许多商店和餐馆都位于这些道路的两侧。结果是，人们常常感觉新加坡是一座为汽车而建的城市，尽管汽车保有量相当低。</p><p>事实上，美国人对这样的大道有一个词：“stroads”。 “stroad”<a href="https://www.strongtowns.org/journal/2018/3/1/whats-a-stroad-and-why-does-it-matter">由城市主义非营利组织 Strong Towns 创造</a>，指的是一条宽阔的高速路，行人也可以沿着这条路散步和购物。美国的情况比新加坡差，但新加坡也有不少。</p><p>关于新加坡为何选择这种发展模式的理论有很多——有人说这是卡车运输和物流所必需的，也有人说政府优先考虑富裕车主的利益。与我交谈过的人甚至表示，在新加坡动荡的早期历史中，宽阔的街道被认为有助于控制骚乱。无论如何，在一个以行人为中心的城市里，有如此多的土地面积供汽车使用，这很奇怪。</p><p>解决这个问题的方法是拓宽人行道。人行道狭窄的道路对行人来说感觉不安全，因为你离汽车太近了。它还使行人与汽车尾气密切接触。这对于散步来说并不是特别好： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg" width="512" height="680" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:680,&quot;width&quot;:512,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:113647,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e727a78-5936-4e97-b97e-82711812e843_512x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>拓宽这些人行道将使人们远离汽车，并允许安装栏杆和其他障碍物，让人们有一种受到保护的感觉，免受汽车的冲撞。这可能需要牺牲一些交通车道，但是哦，好吧。</p><p>这是新加坡更适合行人的街道的一个很好的例子： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7e48c842-2c2e-405a-8c2c-c7e81d4dbac2_678x676.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_