Size&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:800,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:430573,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff475f985-1965-44f6-9d8f-f7dfa35ecd98_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>我刚刚完成了在爱尔兰小城市基尔肯尼（Kilkenny）的年度节日参加<a href="http://kilkenomics.com/">Kilkenomics</a> 。 Kilkenomics是一个相当独特的事件，在此事件中，爱尔兰喜剧演员就各种主题采访了外国经济学家和经济评论员。我的采访主要是关于战争和不断变化的全球秩序 - 如今许多人想到的严峻主题。在这种情况下，我试图尽我所能，主要是通过取笑英国人。总而言之，这是我强烈推荐的经历。</p><p>但是我在基尔肯尼（Kilkenny）的逗留开车回家一个事实，我在智力水平上知道，但从未经历过：爱尔兰是一个非常富有的国家。基尔肯尼（Kilkenny）的小市中心与我在欧洲参观过的任何人一样好，例如一小块奥斯陆，苏黎世或阿姆斯特丹 - 几个小商店，咖啡馆，餐馆，酒吧和百货商店，以及一座旧城堡和一些大教堂在市区以外的地方，景观迅速转移到滚动绿色田野中的单户住宅中以美国风格的单户住宅蔓延。</p><p>这不是我成长时想象的爱尔兰的方式。我对这个国家的心理视野一直是贫穷和冲突的人 - 马铃薯饥荒，一文不见的移民在1800年代淹没了美国海岸，乔纳森·斯威夫特讽刺，詹姆斯·乔伊斯小说，烦恼等等。直到1991年，刻板印象仍然有些真实 - 爱尔兰的人均GDP低于西欧的其他大多数国家。但是16个奇迹之后，情况扭转了： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg" width="1020" height="728" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:728,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:111929,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Ireland's capital is Dublin every year!&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Ireland's capital is Dublin every year!" title="爱尔兰的首都每年都是都柏林！" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F08315a96-45d4-49f0-8af6-fd8f3c02e39e_1020x728.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>当然，您可能已经听说爱尔兰的GDP被夸大了。确实是 - 现在。上图在2007年结束是有充分理由的；如果您查看<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/gdp-per-capita-worldbank?tab=chart&amp;country=USA~DEU~GBR~FRA~KOR~JPN~CHN~IND~IRL">最近的爱尔兰GDP图表</a>，它会飙升至荒谬的高度 - 每人超过100,000美元。这个国家很富有，但不是<em>那么</em>富有。</p><p>经济学家的<a href="https://www.economist.com/the-economist-explains/2023/10/31/whats-weird-about-irelands-gdp">最新文章</a>解释了发生了什么。爱尔兰的GDP被夸大了两个主要原因。首先，也是最重要的是，爱尔兰是著名的税收天堂 - 其低企业所得税率使跨国公司有动力在爱尔兰子公司预订尽可能多的利润。对于欧洲公司而言，这通常需要实际上将其活动转移到爱尔兰，但是美国有一个奇怪的公司税制， <a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/business/economy/explainer-google-and-its-double-irish-tax-scheme-1.4128929">允许Google和Apple等公司</a><a href="https://www.cfr.org/blog/apples-exports-arent-missing-they-are-ireland">参与</a>其他各种<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Double_Irish_arrangement">计划</a><a href="https://static1.squarespace.com/static/562636cfe4b043d43a7492bf/t/58dd39ae2e69cfde1f646716/1490893232477/ProfitShifting.pdf">在爱尔兰预订利润，</a>而无需在该国实际做任何实质性的事情，充气爱尔兰的GDP。第二件怪异是飞机租赁，其统计处理没有很多意义。</p><p>为了停止夸大其GDP，爱尔兰实施了一种特殊的统计系统，称为GNI*或改良的国民收入。爱尔兰的GNI*是其GDP的一半以上。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg" width="688" height="458.6666666666667" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:800,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:77800,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97761b96-6f75-4857-b73a-3ff59da66d49_1200x800.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：爱尔兰<a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-ana/annualnationalaccounts2022/gniandde-globalisedresults/">中央统计局</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>但是，即使这种戏剧性的调整也意味着爱尔兰仍然很丰富。它有500万人，因此其人均GNI*约为54,000美元，比英国人均GDP高出16％，及以上是德国或法国。</p><p> <a href="https://www.economist.com/the-economist-explains/2023/10/31/whats-weird-about-irelands-gdp">正如经济学家所表明的那样</a>，直到2000年，GNI*才真正从GDP开始差异，甚至在2007年，分歧也很小。爱尔兰经济在1990年代和2000年代初的惊人增长非常真实。尽管由于2008年的住房泡沫破裂而受到了<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/why-irelands-housing-bubble-burst">著名的</a>打击，但爱尔兰仍然是世界上最富有的经济体之一的地位。这个国家可能不再是“凯尔特虎”，但在那个光荣的时代中，它的收益似乎很安全。</p><p>爱尔兰也是一个小型精英俱乐部的一部分，该俱乐部比其19世纪的帝国霸主与韩国，波兰，波罗的海以及其他一些国家更富有。轮到英国是破旧的表亲。</p><p>我写了很多关于波兰的文章，每个人都读到韩国。但是爱尔兰是如何做到的？其他国家可以复制这项壮举吗？显然，永远不可能确切地知道为什么一个国家会致富，但是看看历史，我们可以拼凑一个合理的故事。</p><h4>爱尔兰是高科技出口强国</h4><p>我喜欢通过询问每个公司的专门研究来开始这些帖子。解决这个问题的一种好方法是查看出口。爱尔兰的出口向生物医学和制药行业大大加权，还有一些高科技电子制造： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3dfb9e3-879b-4105-b838-da367a52e29b_722x661.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3dfb9e3-879b-4105-b838-da367a52e29b_722x661.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3dfb9e3-879b-4105-b838-da367a52e29b_722x661.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com