a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7cc49269-1f3a-47a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:95961,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7cc49269-1f3a-47a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7cc49269-1f3a-47a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7cc49269-1f3a-47a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7cc49269-1f3a-47a0-b496-c81ffadd8da3_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>换句话说，凯尔特虎看起来很像亚洲老虎队所做的，这个国家生产了许多高科技产品，并将其卖给了世界其他地区。当然，一个国家不能仅靠出口制造业 - 您需要拥有强大的当地经济来散发和<a href="https://eml.berkeley.edu/~moretti/multipliers.pdf">增加</a>出口收入的收益。但是出口制造有多种原因很有用。固有的制造往往会具有快速的生产率增长。许多人认为，通过迫使当地公司在全球市场竞争并帮助他们吸收外国技术，从而<a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/WP/Issues/2019/03/26/The-Return-of-the-Policy-That-Shall-Not-Be-Named-Principles-of-Industrial-Policy-46710">提高了生产率的增长</a>。</p><p>爱尔兰能够实现这一目标的原因之一是它与两个重要经济体的特殊关系：美国和欧洲。</p><h4>来自美国的投资，欧洲的市场</h4><p>如果您想出口很多，则需要在某个地方出售产品。爱尔兰的出口目的地实际上非常多样化： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg" width="636" height="586.6703601108034" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:666,&quot;width&quot;:722,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:636,&quot;bytes&quot;:130828,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F210454e3-9667-4025-82ba-642a5b602592_722x666.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">来源： <a href="https://oec.world/en/profile/country/irl?yearSelector1=2021">OEC</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>欧洲显然是这里最大的，这并不令人惊讶，因为简单的地理位置邻近。但是，爱尔兰是欧盟的一部分，并且在此之前是欧洲经济共同体的一部分，这一事实肯定会有所帮助。爱尔兰对欧洲的拥抱与英国的形成鲜明对比，英国<a href="https://cepr.org/voxeu/columns/impact-brexit-uk-economy-reviewing-evidence">仍在经济上从英国脱欧进行经济上卷起</a>。</p><p>但是，在投资资本方面，爱尔兰在美国（美国）拥有更大的王牌。就像<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-polandmalaysia-model">波兰和马来西亚</a>等最新的发展明星一样，外国直接投资对爱尔兰的经济非常重要。到目前为止，美国是该投资的最大来源。这是来自新西兰外交与贸易部<a href="https://www.mfat.govt.nz/en/trade/mfat-market-reports/foreign-direct-investment-in-ireland-june-2023/">最近的一份报告</a>：</p><blockquote><p>爱尔兰是按人均衡量的欧盟新外国直接投资（FDI）项目最受欢迎的目的地。自1960年代以来，外国直接投资对爱尔兰的吸引力一直是爱尔兰政策的基石，而外国直接投资现在在支持爱尔兰经济方面发挥了非常重要的作用……</p><p>投资主要来自美国，大型爱尔兰侨民在海外有助于促进联系。 2020年，爱尔兰的美国外国直接投资的价格为3900亿美元，比美国总数多于巴西，俄罗斯，印度，中国和南非（金砖国家）合并。尽管受到所有领域的投资受到欢迎，但那些提供出口高价值的产品（例如ICT和Pharma）的人都受到了青睐……</p><p>就全球分销而言，在爱尔兰投资的跨国公司中有847名来自美国，有354家公司是欧洲起源 - 几乎一半来自德国和法国的公司，有136家是英国原产地客户公司，其余212家来自其他公司世界的[。]</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://www.civitas.org.uk/content/files/industrialpolicyintherepublicofireland.pdf">我读到的一份报告</a>称爱尔兰为“硅谷和欧洲之间的中介”。</p><p>正如该报告所述，美国的侨民很大 - 大约<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irish_Americans">3600万</a>，超过爱尔兰人口本身的七倍。但是，不仅仅是侨民在美国和爱尔兰之间建立了联系 - 这是侨民的<em>想法</em>。由于爱尔兰人是成立之后的第一波外国工人来到美国的大浪潮，所以他们的故事是美国作为移民国家的自我认同的基础。许多没有爱尔兰血统的美国人喜欢想象他们这样做， <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Americans_of_Irish_descent#:~:text=At%20least%2022%20presidents%20of,has%20strong%20documented%20Irish%20origins.">例如，比尔·克林顿（Bill Clinton）</a> ，他们声称爱尔兰人的根源永远无法得到证实。在圣帕特里克节，每个人都喝醉了。</p><p>祖先和情感依恋的结合显示了强大的侨民的力量。几个世纪以来，爱尔兰传统上将<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irish_diaspora">其年轻人派往国外的年轻人</a>倾向是一个弱点。自1990年以来，爱尔兰一直是对移民如何飞旋镖并最终成为一种优势的对象课程。</p><h4>爱尔兰政策做到了这一切</h4><p>粗略地说，发展政策有三种。这些都是：</p><ul><li><p>自由化</p></li><li><p>能力建设</p></li><li><p>产业政策</p></li></ul><p>自由化只是意味着消除经济活动的障碍 - 高税，监管，贸易障碍等。能力建设意味着投资于教育，健康和基础设施之类的事情。从补贴出口到向外国投资到促进特定行业，工业政策可能意味着许多不同的事情。</p><p>关于这些方法的争论的人溢出了很多墨水，但是当您查看开发成功案例时，它们都倾向于涉及每种方法的一部分。爱尔兰也不例外。</p><p>爱尔兰的自由化之旅始于早期。即使在1950年代，爱尔兰主要出口农产品，其领导人<a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/42912423">也认识到国外市场的关键程度</a>。在1970年代，像<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T._K._Whitaker">TK Whitaker</a>这样的经济政策影响者成功地争辩了自由贸易 - 如果您是一个没有大部分国内市场的小国，这至关重要。当然，EEC和欧盟对此至关重要。实际上，小国比大国的一个大增长优势可能只是贸易开放性。在一个小国家，每个人都意识到国内市场还不够。</p><p>爱尔兰还具有较低的公司税率，这是其作为避税天堂声誉的一部分（另一部分是一些奇怪的税收漏洞）。但是实际上，情况并非总是如此。直到90年代后期，爱尔兰除了制造业外，各种公司收入的税率<em>很高</em>，该税率非常低： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg" width="600" height="580" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:580,&quot;width&quot;:600,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60359,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26187d30-ffa9-4349-8202-3100904216c2_600x580.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">由英国融资 -<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=74620395">自己的工作</a>，CC BY -SA 4.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>这是自由化和工业政策的结合。制造业的优先低率有助于将经济活动偏向电子和制药等事物；没有这种拆分率，爱尔兰可能会像英国一样成为财务的繁重。</p><p>实际上，人们想知道是否削减其他类型的公司收入的税率可能会无意中将爱尔兰的投资从凯尔特老虎时期的优势转移到诸如住房投机和避税避风港恶作剧之类的事情上。但这也是税收天堂<a href="https://www.journals.uchicago.edu/doi/abs/10.1086/tpe.19.20061896">往往比其他国家的增长速度更快</a>。部分原因可能是许多税收制度仅允许公司实际上将工厂移至该国，因此可以利用一个国家的低税率。因此，爱尔兰可能会通过吸引税收套利的公司来吸收外国技术。</p><p>部分是由于低税率和其他各种业务友好政策的结果，爱尔兰经常在各种“竞争力”排名中排名最高；在2023年， <a href="https://www.imd.org/centers/wcc/world-competitiveness-center/rankings/world-competitiveness-ranking/2023/">在IMD的全球名单上排名第二</a>，仅次于丹麦，在“业务效率”和“政府效率”方面特别高。</p><p>像Ha-Joon Chang这样的一些思想家对FDI作为发展的驱动力都担心。他们担心外国公司不会放弃自己的最佳技术，而外国品牌会挤出国内品牌，最终将一个国家的提升限制在价值链中。 Irish policymakers have shared this concern, <a href="https://www.civitas.org.uk/content/files/industrialpolicyintherepublicofireland.pdf">making various attempts</a> to promote domestic innovation. So far it&#39;s not clear how effective this has been (especially because Ireland&#39;s tax shenanigans make macro data difficult to assess).</p><p> And of course to build a rich economy, one thing you definitely need is a lot of skilled labor. There are two ways to get skilled labor — education and immigration — and in general you should use both. Ireland did. Its baby boom was bigger and lasted much longer than other rich countries: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:169711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5310ac3c-b7a5-4791-81a1-428171e54811_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p> Ireland has also done a great job of educating its young people, with <a href="https://data.oecd.org/eduatt/population-with-tertiary-education.htm">one of the highest rates</a> of tertiary education in the OECD.</p><p> But Ireland has also imported large numbers of workers. In the 90s, a traditional pattern of outmigration reversed, and people started moving to Ireland en masse: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg" width="900" height="578" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:578,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:113626,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F215e8c2c-776d-4ca5-96fa-67e7928990b0_900x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Source: <a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">CSO Ireland</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> These immigrants tend to skew young. And they&#39;re disproportionately high-skilled; in 2022, more than half of immigrants to Ireland <a href="https://mcginleylaw.ie/irish-immigration-statistics-2023/#:~:text=Over%2050%25%20of%20immigrants%20had,those%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20Ireland.">had a university degree or similar</a> . Some of this is <a href="https://personal.lse.ac.uk/minns/minns_jssisi_2005.pdf">natural self-selection</a> , but Ireland also has policies in place to promote skilled immigration.</p><p> They also come from a mix of countries. Ireland&#39;s Central Statistics Office <a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">found that in 2022</a> there were 141,600 total immigrants, 29,600 of whom were returning Irish citizens. About 26,000 were from the EU, about 42,000 from Ukraine, 4800 from the UK, and about 39,000 from other countries.</p><p> At a time when many countries are becoming hostile to immigration or at least questioning its value, Ireland has generally continued to embrace foreign workers. There are some signs that East European immigrants <a href="https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/14782804.2022.2090321">aren&#39;t quite as successful</a> as their West European and global counterparts, and I did encounter a couple instances of stereotypes being leveled at East Europeans during my stay in Kilkenny. In the last year there has been a small <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/mar/21/ireland-anti-refugee-protests-far-right-uk-politics">backlash against refugees</a> .</p><p> But overall, Irish people are consistently <a href="https://odi.org/en/publications/public-narratives-and-attitudes-towards-refugees-and-other-migrants-ireland-country-profile/">more positive about immigration</a> than almost <a href="https://heartsandminds.odi.digital/country?country=ie">anyone else in Europe</a> . And for what it&#39;s worth, my brief personal experience bore this out. Irish people I talked to seemed very aware of how important foreign workers — especially skilled workers — had been to their country&#39;s economic ascent. Some mentioned pub culture and sports as key mechanisms of cultural integration. Others opined that Ireland was a “high EQ country”, whose people specialized in managing top engineers from all over the world. Nobody I talked to seemed to regard Irish immigration policy as anything other than a smashing success.</p><p> In other words, there are a lot of things Ireland did to try to produce an economic miracle. It liberalized its trade policy, cut taxes, created a favorable climate for business, and drew in a bunch of immigrants. But it also encouraged manufacturing, tried to promote domestic innovation, and invested heavily in education. Ireland did it all, and somehow, it worked out.</p><h4> What next for the Celtic Tiger?</h4><p> Ireland&#39;s biggest policy challenge right now, without a doubt, is housing. Rapid immigration, along with replacement-level fertility, has sparked a population boom: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg" width="913" height="576" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:576,&quot;width&quot;:913,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65516,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1525780b-17f3-467c-9059-d32c861a305b_913x576.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Source: <a href="https://www.cso.ie/en/releasesandpublications/ep/p-pme/populationandmigrationestimatesapril2023/keyfindings/">CSO Ireland</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> But this boom <a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/ireland/housing-planning/2023/03/23/irelands-housing-crisis-facts-and-figures-all-you-need-to-know/">hasn&#39;t been matched</a> by a boom in new housing construction. Ireland is still extremely wedded to the idea of single-family homes; very little of the population lives in apartments. The country&#39;&#39;s permitting process is possibly <a href="https://www.thefitzwilliam.com/p/a-simple-and-elegant-response-to">even more onerous</a> than America&#39;s; I met some YIMBYs who had come to Ireland to study the country&#39;s mistakes.</p><p> Housing is regularly listed as <a href="https://www.mfat.govt.nz/en/trade/mfat-market-reports/foreign-direct-investment-in-ireland-june-2023/">the biggest challenge</a> to continued FDI in Ireland, and overcrowding is probably one reason why anti-immigrant politics have finally made it to Ireland&#39;s shores. If the issue doesn&#39;t get solved, it&#39;s not inconceivable that Ireland could follow <a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/why-britain-doesnt-build">Britain into genteel decline</a> .</p><p> But for now, Ireland is still riding high on the success of its Celtic Tiger era. A country that was once subjugated and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anti-Irish_sentiment">looked down upon</a> by its neighbors is now a beacon of wealth and high-tech skill.</p><p> And I think this teaches us a crucial lesson about national development. If you went back to 1923 and asked people whether Ireland would be richer than the UK in a hundred years, how many of them do you think would have said yes? How many would have laughed in your face? And yet here we are, a century later, and that&#39;s the reality. Now pull out a map of the world, and pick out some countries that most people think don&#39;t have what it takes to get rich. Where do you think those countries will be in 100 years?</p><p>你确定吗？ </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button